                      <td valign="top" height="100%"><font face="verdana" size="2" color="white"><span class="spnMessageText" id="msg"> At your level, tap-tanking is the best way to go. Getting defensive skills up is always a big bonus. Your actual melee ability will never amount to much.<br /><br />Though Int is your primary stat, you should focus more on HP and mana and learn to manage with your lich spells. <br /><br />Aggro-kiting might be better than fear kiting, if that's too mana intensive. There's a much better fear spell at (29? or 34?). At your level range, try LoIO and work your way to the windmill. At 24 you can take on the skelly ruins near there.</span id="msg"></font></td>
