                      <td valign="top" height="100%"><font face="verdana" size="2" color="white"><span class="spnMessageText" id="msg"> I dislike Paludel and I solo all the time, so at 20 I went to Lake of Ill Omen.  It's full of undead and pretty easy mobs.  You can fear kite or tap/tank all day long here without running out of mobs :)  Right now at 25 I live at the house of warbones just down from the windmill.  As a dark elf, the only drawback is that I can't sell in this zone.  It's not a money pit but you can make a few plat.  Also goblins here drop skins and salts that you can save up for a really good Chardok quest if you so choose.</span id="msg"></font></td>
